10:54.321 --> 10:55.280
with a Ferris wheel.

10:55.322 --> 10:56.573
Are we in trouble?

10:56.615 --> 10:58.366
No. The last bus

10:56.615 --> 10:58.366
leaves in 20 minutes.

10:58.408 --> 11:00.701
We just have to get outside

10:58.408 --> 11:00.701
and wait for it.

